  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CBarrier\uFF1E \n[On Play] [When Digivolving] \uFF1CRecovery
    +1 (Deck)\uFF1E. Then, if during an attack, 1 of your Digimon in the breeding
    area may digivolve into a level 6 or lower [Chronicle]\_trait Digimon card in
